1
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:37,440
=Have a Crush on You=

2
00:01:38,220 --> 00:01:40,980
=Episode 3=

3
00:02:06,895 --> 00:02:07,736
You're awake?

4
00:02:09,216 --> 00:02:10,336
Oh, that was quick.

5
00:02:17,815 --> 00:02:18,576
I'm off.

6
00:02:18,576 --> 00:02:19,455
I will see you off.

7
00:02:19,576 --> 00:02:20,216
No need.

8
00:02:20,375 --> 00:02:21,416
I have come all the way here.

9
00:02:34,095 --> 00:02:34,895
Let me carry them.

10
00:02:56,576 --> 00:02:57,216
You're leaving soon.

11
00:02:57,216 --> 00:02:58,095
Do you have nothing to say?

12
00:02:58,576 --> 00:02:59,655
What should I say?

13
00:02:59,856 --> 00:03:00,496
Anything.

14
00:03:01,136 --> 00:03:01,856
Maybe you can tell me

15
00:03:01,856 --> 00:03:03,375
your feeling about this trip.

16
00:03:05,976 --> 00:03:07,015
Should I say,

17
00:03:07,015 --> 00:03:08,655
"I'm happy to see you here again"?

18
00:03:08,895 --> 00:03:11,175
It depends on whether
that feeling is genuine or not.

19
00:03:12,976 --> 00:03:14,735
It's a shock rather than a surprise.

20
00:03:17,496 --> 00:03:17,976
It's yours.

21
00:03:18,136 --> 00:03:18,615
Thanks.

22
00:03:19,940 --> 00:03:24,700
♪However, we never♪

23
00:03:25,375 --> 00:03:27,696
It seems to be a wise decision
to get a divorce back then.

24
00:03:28,535 --> 00:03:29,655
We feel the same way.

25
00:03:33,175 --> 00:03:33,895
I'm leaving.

26
00:03:41,255 --> 00:03:42,095
Safe trip.

27
00:03:44,976 --> 00:03:45,720
Thanks.

28
