32
00:03:57,220 --> 00:04:01,620
♪Yet suffer in regrets♪

33
00:04:01,620 --> 00:04:03,460
♪Choosing a direction♪

34
00:04:03,460 --> 00:04:05,780
♪At the next crossroad♪

35
00:04:05,780 --> 00:04:09,580
♪Is like separating the universe♪

36
00:04:10,936 --> 00:04:12,336
(2012 Jiangzhou, China)
Sorry, I'm late.

37
00:04:12,416 --> 00:04:13,895
It's cool. I just got here.

38
00:04:14,216 --> 00:04:16,616
I ordered you a cold brew and a dessert.

39
00:04:16,736 --> 00:04:18,095
Hope you will like it.

40
00:04:18,655 --> 00:04:19,935
I want coffee.

41
00:04:21,535 --> 00:04:23,215
Cold brew is a type of coffee.

42
00:04:25,535 --> 00:04:26,255
Why don't you try it?

43
00:04:32,896 --> 00:04:33,495
How does it taste?

44
00:04:35,375 --> 00:04:36,215
Good.

45
00:04:40,696 --> 00:04:41,896
Zhiqian...

46
00:04:44,456 --> 00:04:45,655
Is he faring well?

47
00:04:47,375 --> 00:04:49,495
He goes into a frenzy

48
00:04:49,495 --> 00:04:50,535
of jogging and drinking every day.

49
00:04:55,136 --> 00:04:55,775
Dong.

50
00:04:56,136 --> 00:04:57,255
I don't understand

51
00:04:57,416 --> 00:04:58,976
why you would fall for another guy.

52
00:04:59,176 --> 00:05:00,095
Ning is a really good guy

53
00:05:00,136 --> 00:05:01,535
and he likes you very much.

54
00:05:03,976 --> 00:05:05,095
I said this before.

55
00:05:05,416 --> 00:05:09,815
Both arts and the human mind
pursue freedom.

56
00:05:10,576 --> 00:05:11,896
I couldn't control

57
00:05:13,095 --> 00:05:14,416
whom I fall in love with.

58
00:05:17,416 --> 00:05:20,456
Well, medical students
can't understand arts.

59
00:05:21,215 --> 00:05:23,775
We uphold the principle of determination

60
00:05:23,775 --> 00:05:24,815
and perseverance.

61
00:05:27,576 --> 00:05:28,335
Liuzheng.

62
00:05:28,856 --> 00:05:31,896
You are quite different from
what I thought about you.

63
00:05:33,775 --> 00:05:34,775
Dong.

64
00:05:35,495 --> 00:05:37,176
I feel the same about you too.

65
00:05:43,016 --> 00:05:45,255
Where does he usually
go for a drink at night?

66
00:05:47,655 --> 00:05:48,896
I'm not going to tell you.

67
00:05:49,375 --> 00:05:52,136
Even so, I will find it out

68
00:05:52,215 --> 00:05:53,215
as long as I want to.

69
00:06:26,136 --> 00:06:27,535
Isn't that your usual spot?

70
00:06:27,976 --> 00:06:30,136
Why do you sit here today?

71
00:06:30,775 --> 00:06:31,655
You knew?

72
00:06:31,976 --> 00:06:33,976
I have seen you a while ago, silly girl.

73
00:06:37,935 --> 00:06:38,696
Excuse me.

74
00:06:38,976 --> 00:06:40,296
A glass, please.

75
00:06:40,976 --> 00:06:42,255
(Hi, your glass.)

76
00:06:44,296 --> 00:06:45,416
I'm really curious about this.

77
00:06:45,456 --> 00:06:48,215
Are you here to keep watch on me?

78
00:06:49,935 --> 00:06:51,736
I'm worried you might do
something silly.

79
00:06:51,736 --> 00:06:53,016
Something silly?

80
00:06:54,255 --> 00:06:55,255
Do you mean to commit suicide?

81
00:06:55,815 --> 00:06:57,856
Continuous drinking
is similar to slow suicide.

82
00:07:06,616 --> 00:07:07,495
Tastes good?

83
00:07:08,335 --> 00:07:09,176
Good.

84
00:07:20,535 --> 00:07:21,136
Ruan Liuzheng.

85
00:07:21,136 --> 00:07:22,375
What do you want from me?

86
00:07:24,616 --> 00:07:25,976
I just want to keep your company.

87
00:07:27,055 --> 00:07:30,616
I have a very effective method
to heal your broken heart.

88
00:07:30,696 --> 00:07:31,535
Do you want to know about it?

89
00:07:35,495 --> 00:07:35,935
Fire away.

90
00:07:36,935 --> 00:07:37,616
Cry.

91
00:07:39,176 --> 00:07:40,535
Cry out loud.

92
00:07:40,775 --> 00:07:44,296
My friends used to cry a lot

93
00:07:44,296 --> 00:07:45,495
after their breakups.

94
00:07:45,495 --> 00:07:46,576
Cry as much as you can. Cry a river.

95
00:07:46,815 --> 00:07:48,775
You can wail or bawl.

96
00:07:49,215 --> 00:07:50,655
You become so talkative after drinking.

97
00:07:52,495 --> 00:07:53,535
You don't have to believe me.

98
00:08:01,856 --> 00:08:05,255
Do you know
why I have a deep interest in medicine?

99
00:08:07,416 --> 00:08:11,176
Because everything is
with traceable clues.

100
00:08:11,416 --> 00:08:13,896
As long as you keep exploring it,

101
00:08:13,896 --> 00:08:15,696
the answer will be revealed eventually.

102
00:08:15,696 --> 00:08:18,375
But love relationships
don't have an exact answer.

103
00:08:18,375 --> 00:08:21,535
People cheat for no reason.

104
00:08:21,535 --> 00:08:22,255
It's just unexpected.

105
00:08:22,255 --> 00:08:23,535
You know absolutely nothing.

106
00:08:23,535 --> 00:08:24,616
They just fall out of love
for no reason.

107
00:08:24,655 --> 00:08:26,215
Is that even reasonable?

108
00:08:26,215 --> 00:08:27,416
You know nothing at all.

109
00:08:27,416 --> 00:08:28,896
So, you know more than I do?

110
00:08:28,896 --> 00:08:32,215
Had you spent effort
to manage the relationship

111
00:08:32,215 --> 00:08:35,215
like you did on the study,

112
00:08:35,335 --> 00:08:37,455
things wouldn't have
panned out this way.

113
00:08:39,056 --> 00:08:39,856
Do you know that?

114
00:08:40,736 --> 00:08:41,976
Have you heard this saying before?

115
00:08:42,176 --> 00:08:46,296
"Vigorous river water runs eastward,

116
00:08:46,416 --> 00:08:49,775
carrying away waves along
with the heroes.

117
00:08:51,176 --> 00:08:54,616
Fame and glory are
but a worldly illusion.

118
00:08:54,616 --> 00:08:57,376
As long as the mountain remains green,

119
00:08:58,095 --> 00:08:59,895
the eternal scarlet sunset
can be witnessed."

120
00:09:00,736 --> 00:09:02,256
Can you interpret this?

121
00:09:02,736 --> 00:09:03,655
Sure. Listen carefully.

122
00:09:05,296 --> 00:09:06,816
Stop drinking.

123
00:09:07,936 --> 00:09:09,296
In nature,

124
00:09:09,376 --> 00:09:15,655
everyone is destined
to experience betrayal.

125
00:09:21,580 --> 00:09:23,980
(No Climbing. Stay Safe.)

126
00:10:09,736 --> 00:10:10,655
You're up.

127
00:10:23,135 --> 00:10:24,095
Ning.

128
00:10:30,095 --> 00:10:31,256
Why are we here?

129
00:10:31,416 --> 00:10:32,895
You can't remember anything
about last night?

130
00:10:36,655 --> 00:10:37,856
You were so drunk yesterday.

131
00:10:38,015 --> 00:10:39,575
I wanted to send you back to the dorm.

132
00:10:39,856 --> 00:10:41,455
But the gate was closed
when we reached there.

133
00:10:41,936 --> 00:10:43,015
So, I could only take you here

134
00:10:43,056 --> 00:10:43,856
and make do with it.

135
00:10:45,176 --> 00:10:46,215
Thank you.

136
00:10:46,496 --> 00:10:47,335
Drink some water.

137
00:10:48,736 --> 00:10:49,575
I didn't leave

138
00:10:49,575 --> 00:10:50,655
because I was afraid

139
00:10:50,655 --> 00:10:51,736
you would be choked

140
00:10:51,736 --> 00:10:52,655
on your own vomit.

141
00:10:53,095 --> 00:10:54,936
I used to encounter such cases

142
00:10:54,936 --> 00:10:56,256
when I was in the emergency department.

143
00:10:57,176 --> 00:10:57,816
Thank you.

144
00:11:01,340 --> 00:11:03,410
(Hai Yue Home)

145
00:11:03,416 --> 00:11:04,135
Fret not.

146
00:11:04,335 --> 00:11:05,496
This T-shirt belongs to the waitress.

147
00:11:05,775 --> 00:11:06,455
She changed this for you

148
00:11:06,455 --> 00:11:07,455
because your vomit stained your shirt.

149
00:11:08,095 --> 00:11:09,856
Remember to return her this

150
00:11:09,856 --> 00:11:10,736
after washing it.

151
00:11:15,135 --> 00:11:16,015
I'll wait for you at the door.

152
00:11:16,015 --> 00:11:16,816
Chop-chop.

153
00:11:34,575 --> 00:11:35,496
That was a nice game.

154
00:11:35,775 --> 00:11:36,575
Did you take the room key?

155
00:11:37,455 --> 00:11:38,376
Isn't that Ning?

156
00:11:38,416 --> 00:11:39,135
Ning.

157
00:11:41,256 --> 00:11:41,976
Ruan Liuzheng?

158
00:11:43,256 --> 00:11:44,176
What are you doing here?

159
00:11:44,856 --> 00:11:45,616
We came here to watch the game

160
00:11:45,616 --> 00:11:46,616
yesterday night.

161
00:11:47,535 --> 00:11:48,376
The lift is over there.

162
00:11:51,695 --> 00:11:52,015
Come on.

163
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:13,280
(Hai Yue Home)

164
00:12:42,455 --> 00:12:43,736
Give me a break.

165
00:12:46,616 --> 00:12:47,775
Medical students should
have this knowledge though.

166
00:12:47,775 --> 00:12:48,455
Hurry up and stand up.

167
00:12:48,455 --> 00:12:49,335
The heart can't take this.

168
00:12:49,496 --> 00:12:50,095
Hurry up.

169
00:12:52,695 --> 00:12:53,455
Get up.

170
00:12:56,736 --> 00:12:57,496
I feel like

171
00:12:57,816 --> 00:12:58,496
I'm going to die.

172
00:12:58,655 --> 00:12:59,616
Don't just stand there. Move.

173
00:13:01,215 --> 00:13:02,135
Stand up. Come on.

174
00:13:02,775 --> 00:13:03,976
You're going for a drink tonight, right?

175
00:13:04,015 --> 00:13:04,496
Go prepare for it.

176
00:13:04,496 --> 00:13:05,416
Stop jogging. Go back

177
00:13:05,416 --> 00:13:06,176
and get a shower.

178
00:13:06,616 --> 00:13:07,416
No, I quit the wine.

179
00:13:08,775 --> 00:13:10,256
I'm becoming a resident soon.

180
00:13:10,976 --> 00:13:13,215
The seniors said
the following three years

181
00:13:13,215 --> 00:13:15,535
is the toughest time in our career
as a doctor.

182
00:13:16,256 --> 00:13:17,416
So, I must make sure
I'm in perfect condition.

183
00:13:18,535 --> 00:13:19,296
You can do it.

184
00:13:20,856 --> 00:13:21,655
Thank you.

185
00:13:21,655 --> 00:13:22,655
I've recovered from it.

186
00:13:22,655 --> 00:13:23,816
Thanks for what?

187
00:13:24,015 --> 00:13:26,736
"As long as the mountain remains green,
the eternal sunset can be witnessed."

188
00:13:26,976 --> 00:13:28,015
You told me this.

189
00:13:28,575 --> 00:13:29,575
When?

190
00:13:29,775 --> 00:13:31,816
You said this when you were drunk.
Did you forget about this?

191
00:13:32,816 --> 00:13:33,775
Thanks to your fighting talk,

192
00:13:34,056 --> 00:13:36,056
I will work out for one hour per day.

193
00:13:37,655 --> 00:13:39,176
Work out one hour per day.

194
00:13:39,335 --> 00:13:41,535
To work in perfect health for 50 years.

195
00:13:41,616 --> 00:13:43,535
To work in perfect health for 100 years.

196
00:13:43,816 --> 00:13:44,736
100 years?

197
00:13:44,816 --> 00:13:46,095
And lead a happy life.

198
00:13:46,256 --> 00:13:48,095
And lead a happy life.

199
00:13:48,296 --> 00:13:49,176
- Come on.
- Come on!

200
00:13:51,816 --> 00:13:53,296
Ning, you can do it!

201
00:14:08,095 --> 00:14:09,496
Ning is having an affair
with that woman.

202
00:14:12,736 --> 00:14:13,535
You better stop that.

203
00:14:21,695 --> 00:14:22,816
There are rumors that

204
00:14:22,816 --> 00:14:25,015
you and Ning Zhiqian
went to a hotel together.

205
00:14:25,056 --> 00:14:26,655
Why don't you explain it?

206
00:14:26,655 --> 00:14:27,856
How?

207
00:14:28,095 --> 00:14:28,736
They wouldn't believe me

208
00:14:28,736 --> 00:14:30,056
even if I try hard to explain.

209
00:14:30,296 --> 00:14:31,015
Hurry up and eat.

210
00:14:31,736 --> 00:14:32,496
True though.

211
00:14:32,736 --> 00:14:34,296
If I hadn't known you
for almost 20 years,

212
00:14:34,296 --> 00:14:35,135
I wouldn't buy it either.

213
00:14:36,256 --> 00:14:38,736
But their words are too hurtful to hear.

214
00:14:39,015 --> 00:14:40,376
They said that you have an affair

215
00:14:40,535 --> 00:14:41,856
with Ning Zhiqian.

216
00:14:42,176 --> 00:14:43,416
If you really have nothing
to do with him,

217
00:14:43,416 --> 00:14:45,775
stay from him as far as possible.

218
00:14:46,376 --> 00:14:47,135
My conscience is clear.

219
00:14:47,135 --> 00:14:48,416
Why should I stay away from him?

220
00:14:48,936 --> 00:14:49,535
Hurry up and eat.

221
00:14:51,095 --> 00:14:52,376
You're right.

222
00:14:52,575 --> 00:14:53,376
Well, never mind that.

223
00:14:53,416 --> 00:14:54,575
I have good news to tell you.

224
00:14:55,655 --> 00:14:57,056
I landed my internship

225
00:14:57,496 --> 00:14:58,655
at Beiya Hospital.

226
00:14:59,056 --> 00:14:59,775
For real?

227
00:14:59,775 --> 00:15:00,135
Yes.

228
00:15:01,215 --> 00:15:01,575
Treat me to a big meal.

229
00:15:02,095 --> 00:15:03,335
Let's not celebrate this first.

230
00:15:03,335 --> 00:15:03,976
What about you?

231
00:15:08,895 --> 00:15:10,056
Well, eat as much as you can.

232
00:15:10,296 --> 00:15:11,895
You can have all the big pieces.

233
00:15:11,895 --> 00:15:12,655
Eat more.

234
00:15:13,335 --> 00:15:13,736
Eat up.

235
00:15:13,775 --> 00:15:15,256
And you can have small pieces.

236
