(2019 Jiangzhou, China)

237
00:15:23,060 --> 00:15:26,260
(Arrive at the exit)

238
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:31,560
(Did you take my charging cable?)

239
00:15:31,560 --> 00:15:32,610
(Check if it's with you.)

240
00:15:36,575 --> 00:15:38,215
I didn't take your thing.

241
00:15:38,296 --> 00:15:39,455
You better look for it yourself.

242
00:15:43,335 --> 00:15:45,056
(I didn't take your thing.)

243
00:15:45,056 --> 00:15:46,535
(You better look for it yourself.)

244
00:15:48,296 --> 00:15:49,015
Mr. Ning.

245
00:15:49,015 --> 00:15:50,655
Isn't your charging cable
right before you?

246
00:15:52,775 --> 00:15:53,655
Mr. Ning.

247
00:15:53,856 --> 00:15:55,816
If you want to know
whether she arrived safely,

248
00:15:55,816 --> 00:15:56,856
just ask her directly.

249
00:15:57,135 --> 00:15:58,176
Mind your own business.

250
00:15:58,176 --> 00:15:59,215
Keep your meddling nose out
of my affairs.

251
00:15:59,775 --> 00:16:00,416
It's almost time

252
00:16:00,416 --> 00:16:01,335
to go for the rounds.

253
00:16:01,376 --> 00:16:02,335
I know.

254
00:16:11,380 --> 00:16:13,300
(Ning Zhiqian)

255
00:16:13,300 --> 00:16:16,260
(Delete)

256
00:16:18,820 --> 00:16:19,940
(Delete the contact)

257
00:16:24,960 --> 00:16:26,000
(Two months later)

258
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:28,540
(West District Hospital of Jiangzhou)

259
00:16:28,540 --> 00:16:29,320
(President's Office)

260
00:16:29,335 --> 00:16:29,895
Come on in.

261
00:16:31,496 --> 00:16:32,496
President Wang, why do you ask for me?

262
00:16:32,775 --> 00:16:33,775
Go get changed.

263
00:16:33,775 --> 00:16:34,816
Let's go to the airport.

264
00:16:35,056 --> 00:16:35,856
Airport?

265
00:16:36,535 --> 00:16:37,135
President Wang.

266
00:16:37,416 --> 00:16:39,296
I'm sorry to let you down

267
00:16:39,296 --> 00:16:40,895
as I failed to bring Mr. Zhao
back from Dahl last time.

268
00:16:41,256 --> 00:16:43,575
Zhiqian told me about this.
It wasn't your fault.

269
00:16:44,135 --> 00:16:45,296
He told me

270
00:16:45,296 --> 00:16:47,736
that Mr. Zhao is healing nicely
these two months.

271
00:16:47,976 --> 00:16:49,335
Really? That's great.

272
00:16:50,895 --> 00:16:52,816
Are you close to Dr. Ning?

273
00:16:53,135 --> 00:16:54,335
His mother, Wen Yi

274
00:16:54,376 --> 00:16:55,895
was my bosom friend for decades.

275
00:16:56,575 --> 00:16:58,535
Sadly, she passed away
in an accident in Africa.

276
00:16:58,775 --> 00:17:00,816
She didn't get to attend
her son's wedding

277
00:17:00,816 --> 00:17:02,215
and meet her daughter-in-law.

278
00:17:03,015 --> 00:17:04,575
Life is full of uncertainty.

279
00:17:08,496 --> 00:17:09,376
Mr. Zhao.

280
00:17:10,496 --> 00:17:10,935
President Wang.

281
00:17:10,935 --> 00:17:11,575
Mr. Zhao.

282
00:17:12,616 --> 00:17:13,575
Oh, my. President Wang.

283
00:17:13,575 --> 00:17:14,256
Nice to see you again, Mr. Zhao.

284
00:17:14,776 --> 00:17:16,055
Your complexion is good.

285
00:17:16,575 --> 00:17:17,256
Thank you.

286
00:17:17,256 --> 00:17:18,896
You look younger than you did
before you went to Africa.

287
00:17:19,175 --> 00:17:21,016
Thanks to Dr. Ding.

288
00:17:32,335 --> 00:17:33,616
You're back too, Zhiqian.

289
00:17:35,055 --> 00:17:35,976
How do you feel recently?

290
00:17:35,976 --> 00:17:36,815
I must get a good look at you.

291
00:17:36,856 --> 00:17:37,736
I'm good here.

292
00:17:38,055 --> 00:17:39,415
Nutritional science is my expertise.

293
00:17:39,415 --> 00:17:40,496
I'm in tip-top shape.

294
00:17:41,520 --> 00:17:42,080
Pretty good.

295
00:17:44,695 --> 00:17:45,575
Mr. Zhao.

296
00:17:45,616 --> 00:17:47,295
I booked a table at Wangyue Restaurant.

297
00:17:47,295 --> 00:17:48,856
Let's have a meal together

298
00:17:48,856 --> 00:17:49,815
to welcome your return.

299
00:17:50,215 --> 00:17:52,415
I'm kind of tired

300
00:17:52,815 --> 00:17:53,695
after the long flight.

301
00:17:54,055 --> 00:17:55,016
What about this?

302
00:17:55,215 --> 00:17:57,175
Dr. Ning will go on my behalf.

303
00:17:57,896 --> 00:17:59,376
Let's meet up someday.

304
00:17:59,376 --> 00:18:00,295
I will treat you to a meal.

305
00:18:00,536 --> 00:18:01,935
- What do you say?
- Sure.

306
00:18:02,616 --> 00:18:04,215
You may go home and take a rest.

307
00:18:04,616 --> 00:18:05,335
Zhiqian.

308
00:18:05,376 --> 00:18:05,935
You should go.

309
00:18:05,935 --> 00:18:06,496
Sure.

310
00:18:06,496 --> 00:18:08,095
Ruan, walk with Dr. Ning.

311
00:18:10,896 --> 00:18:11,295
Give it to me.

312
00:18:11,295 --> 00:18:11,695
No need.

313
00:18:11,896 --> 00:18:12,496
Give it to me.

314
00:18:21,095 --> 00:18:21,896
Thank you.

315
00:18:23,616 --> 00:18:24,295
Please enjoy your meal.

316
00:18:27,815 --> 00:18:28,656
Zhiqian.

317
00:18:28,935 --> 00:18:30,295
I'm driving today.

318
00:18:30,295 --> 00:18:31,095
I can't drink.

319
00:18:32,175 --> 00:18:32,896
Dr. Ruan.

320
00:18:33,335 --> 00:18:34,896
Drink to Zhiqian for me.

321
00:18:37,175 --> 00:18:37,815
Sure.

322
00:18:37,935 --> 00:18:39,256
Can Dr. Ruan drink?

323
00:18:39,256 --> 00:18:39,935
Don't force her.

324
00:18:40,656 --> 00:18:42,575
She holds her alcohol well.

325
00:18:45,016 --> 00:18:45,695
Dr. Ning.

326
00:18:46,055 --> 00:18:46,976
I will drink to you.

327
00:18:49,496 --> 00:18:50,455
-Thank you.
-Alright.

328
00:18:50,616 --> 00:18:51,935
I will drink juice.

329
00:19:03,376 --> 00:19:04,095
Hello.

330
00:19:04,776 --> 00:19:05,575
Mr. Chen.

331
00:19:05,976 --> 00:19:07,215
Hold on.

332
00:19:07,856 --> 00:19:08,815
It's the hospital.

333
00:19:08,815 --> 00:19:09,776
You eat first.

334
00:19:17,256 --> 00:19:18,575
Dr. Wu isn't back this time?

335
00:19:18,736 --> 00:19:19,656
He came back last month.

336
00:19:23,656 --> 00:19:24,976
Why did you delete my contact?

337
00:19:26,175 --> 00:19:27,295
We won't be in touch, anyway.

338
00:19:28,496 --> 00:19:29,455
We're meeting again here.

339
00:19:29,815 --> 00:19:30,695
Give me your contact.

340
00:19:30,976 --> 00:19:31,856
I'll scan your code.

341
00:19:32,256 --> 00:19:33,376
This isn't necessary.

342
00:19:33,976 --> 00:19:34,896
We have nothing to talk about.

343
00:19:39,055 --> 00:19:40,736
You left your pajamas in my room.

344
00:19:41,055 --> 00:19:42,136
I wanted to ask you

345
00:19:42,136 --> 00:19:43,295
if you want me to send it back or...

346
00:19:43,415 --> 00:19:44,736
No need. Throw it away.

347
00:19:45,776 --> 00:19:46,896
Oh, you should've told me.

348
00:19:47,215 --> 00:19:48,095
I have brought it back.

349
00:19:48,095 --> 00:19:48,815
It's in my suitcase.

350
00:19:48,815 --> 00:19:49,736
I will bring it for you later.

351
00:19:52,695 --> 00:19:53,256
Zhiqian.

352
00:19:54,256 --> 00:19:56,935
You know what, both you and Dr. Ruan

353
00:19:57,136 --> 00:19:58,376
are with neurosurgery.

354
00:19:59,856 --> 00:20:01,815
Dr. Ruan told me just now.

355
00:20:02,376 --> 00:20:04,536
When Dr. Ruan first came
to the hospital,

356
00:20:04,695 --> 00:20:06,335
I asked which department
she wanted to choose.

357
00:20:06,656 --> 00:20:08,335
When she said neurosurgery,

358
00:20:08,815 --> 00:20:10,335
I was taken aback by her answer.

359
00:20:10,575 --> 00:20:13,856
She is indeed a tough girl.

360
00:20:14,295 --> 00:20:15,616
About the recent trip to Africa,

361
00:20:15,776 --> 00:20:17,376
she volunteered for it.

362
00:20:18,256 --> 00:20:20,575
We must cultivate

363
00:20:20,575 --> 00:20:22,695
such a go-getter like her, right?

364
00:20:23,976 --> 00:20:24,736
Oh, right.

365
00:20:25,055 --> 00:20:26,496
Beiya Hospital is short-staffed
currently

366
00:20:26,496 --> 00:20:27,856
and requested a secondment

367
00:20:27,856 --> 00:20:29,415
from West District Hospital.

368
00:20:30,335 --> 00:20:32,496
I have been thinking about this.

369
00:20:33,095 --> 00:20:36,575
I want to give this chance to Dr. Ruan.

370
00:20:37,295 --> 00:20:37,896
Really?

371
00:20:38,496 --> 00:20:40,776
It's a good chance for you
to learn there.

372
00:20:43,295 --> 00:20:44,215
Thank you so much.

373
00:20:46,935 --> 00:20:47,815
Zhiqian.

374
00:20:48,256 --> 00:20:50,175
Dr. Ruan is going to Beiya Hospital.

375
00:20:50,376 --> 00:20:52,776
Could you be her mentor?

376
00:20:56,256 --> 00:20:58,215
I'm aware

377
00:20:58,295 --> 00:20:59,736
that you don't simply accept students.

378
00:20:59,896 --> 00:21:02,295
But I can tell you without a doubt

379
00:21:02,376 --> 00:21:03,575
that Dr. Ruan

380
00:21:03,695 --> 00:21:06,776
is a potential top-bracket doctor.

381
00:21:13,496 --> 00:21:14,376
Zhiqian.

382
00:21:14,496 --> 00:21:15,575
As you know,

383
00:21:15,575 --> 00:21:17,976
West District Hospital
lacks good doctors.

384
00:21:17,976 --> 00:21:19,736
Why don't you share my burden

385
00:21:19,736 --> 00:21:20,896
to cultivate the talents?

386
00:21:20,896 --> 00:21:22,175
Fine.

387
00:21:24,335 --> 00:21:25,376
I will guide her.

388
00:21:27,136 --> 00:21:28,896
Ruan, hurry up.

389
00:21:28,935 --> 00:21:30,055
Drink to Dr. Ning.

390
00:21:31,095 --> 00:21:31,815
Yes.

391
00:21:33,736 --> 00:21:34,376
Dr. Ning.

392
00:21:34,656 --> 00:21:35,536
I will drink to you.

393
00:21:36,536 --> 00:21:37,815
Stop calling him Dr. Ning.

394
00:21:37,856 --> 00:21:38,776
That sounds distant.

395
00:21:39,536 --> 00:21:40,175
What should I call him?

396
00:21:40,175 --> 00:21:41,455
Call him Mr. Ning.

397
00:21:44,695 --> 00:21:45,656
Mr. Ning.

398
00:21:45,736 --> 00:21:46,415
Here's to you.

399
00:21:48,335 --> 00:21:48,976
I've finished mine.

400
00:22:07,575 --> 00:22:08,976
Top up his glass.

401
00:22:10,695 --> 00:22:11,496
Sure.

402
00:22:17,616 --> 00:22:18,455
Thank you.

403
00:22:22,415 --> 00:22:23,776
Ask for his contact.

404
00:22:26,095 --> 00:22:27,736
Chop-chop. It's a rare chance.

405
00:22:30,415 --> 00:22:31,055
Sure.

406
00:22:33,856 --> 00:22:34,656
Ask for the contact.

407
00:22:38,656 --> 00:22:39,536
Mr. Ning.

408
00:22:39,896 --> 00:22:40,976
Can we exchange our contacts?

409
00:22:41,695 --> 00:22:42,496
Sure.

410
00:22:45,295 --> 00:22:47,295
May I have your contact code?

411
00:22:49,175 --> 00:22:50,016
Really?

412
00:23:08,420 --> 00:23:09,660
(Ning Zhiqian)

413
00:23:13,095 --> 00:23:15,055
I...I have sent you a friend request.

414
00:23:15,095 --> 00:23:15,935
Please approve it.

415
00:23:41,920 --> 00:23:43,040
(I thought you didn't want my contact.)

416
00:23:50,250 --> 00:23:51,130
(Remember to take your pajamas from me.)

417
00:23:54,335 --> 00:23:55,496
(Zhiqian.)

418
00:23:55,496 --> 00:23:56,136
(Eat more.)

419
00:23:56,136 --> 00:23:57,215
Madam Wang. You too.

420
00:24:07,016 --> 00:24:08,695
Which of these buildings
is his block again?

421
00:24:09,136 --> 00:24:10,496
I can't remember that.

422
00:24:11,175 --> 00:24:11,815
This.

423
00:24:13,856 --> 00:24:14,695
Why did you know about that?

424
00:24:16,695 --> 00:24:17,455
Well,

425
00:24:17,536 --> 00:24:19,215
Mr. Ning mentioned it
before he got into the car.

426
00:24:19,815 --> 00:24:21,095
Block 7 Unit No. 2.

427
00:24:21,095 --> 00:24:22,055
It's written here.

428
00:24:26,736 --> 00:24:27,656
Zhiqian.

429
00:24:28,175 --> 00:24:28,856
We've arrived.

430
00:24:28,856 --> 00:24:30,055
I'm sorry. I fell asleep.

431
00:24:30,616 --> 00:24:31,575
I know you're tired.

432
00:24:32,175 --> 00:24:33,095
Thank you, Madam Wang.

433
00:24:33,295 --> 00:24:34,055
You're welcome.

434
00:24:34,055 --> 00:24:35,175
Oh, I have something for you.

435
00:24:42,095 --> 00:24:44,016
Not now. President Wang is here.

436
00:24:45,976 --> 00:24:47,536
Don't take it out now.

437
00:25:09,695 --> 00:25:10,575
Madam Wang.

438
00:25:10,575 --> 00:25:12,695
I brought you a gift from Africa.

439
00:25:13,496 --> 00:25:14,496
For me?

440
00:25:15,136 --> 00:25:16,215
I won't be shy then.

441
00:25:16,256 --> 00:25:16,935
Thank you.

442
00:25:17,215 --> 00:25:18,455
Don't be so courteous.

443
00:25:18,815 --> 00:25:20,575
You carried this all the way back here.

444
00:25:20,575 --> 00:25:21,175
The suitcase must be very heavy.

445
00:25:21,295 --> 00:25:22,055
I heard that it's a good product.

446
00:25:22,055 --> 00:25:22,776
You can try it.

447
00:25:23,896 --> 00:25:25,536
Let's keep in touch.

448
00:25:26,215 --> 00:25:27,376
Get rest early.

449
00:25:27,496 --> 00:25:28,215
I have zipped the case.

450
00:25:28,215 --> 00:25:29,016
Let me carry it inside.

451
00:25:29,016 --> 00:25:30,175
No need. I can do it myself.

452
00:25:30,175 --> 00:25:31,016
It's fine.

453
00:25:31,295 --> 00:25:32,215
I will get going, then.

454
00:25:37,335 --> 00:25:38,376
Thank you, Dr. Ruan.

455
00:25:38,656 --> 00:25:39,016
Don't mention it.

456
00:25:39,695 --> 00:25:41,095
Get rest early.

457
00:25:42,215 --> 00:25:42,616
Bye-bye.

458
00:25:42,736 --> 00:25:43,136
Bye-bye.

459
00:25:43,976 --> 00:25:44,455
Bye-bye.

460
00:25:44,776 --> 00:25:45,376
Bye-bye.

461
00:25:47,016 --> 00:25:47,536
Ruan.

462
00:25:48,616 --> 00:25:50,575
I remember
your marital status is divorced

463
00:25:51,095 --> 00:25:53,656
when you're filling out the form, right?

464
00:25:56,896 --> 00:25:59,016
Same as Zhiqian.

465
00:25:59,616 --> 00:26:00,616
I see.

466
00:26:00,935 --> 00:26:01,776
Ruan.

467
00:26:02,055 --> 00:26:03,935
Your transfer to Beiya

468
00:26:04,175 --> 00:26:05,536
is a singular opportunity.

469
00:26:06,016 --> 00:26:07,656
You must seize it well.

470
00:26:07,736 --> 00:26:08,455
You must try

471
00:26:08,455 --> 00:26:11,095
to reap success in both career
and love life.

472
00:26:13,976 --> 00:26:15,256
Why so serious?

473
00:26:15,616 --> 00:26:16,736
It's just a joke.

474
00:26:16,736 --> 00:26:17,536
Hop in.

475
00:26:27,130 --> 00:26:28,920
(When are you taking
the pajamas from me?)

476
00:26:31,215 --> 00:26:32,496
Fasten the belt.

477
00:26:52,536 --> 00:26:53,656
Hey, eat something.

478
00:26:53,656 --> 00:26:54,616
Sit down and eat.

479
00:26:55,455 --> 00:26:56,175
It's too late. I need to go now.

480
00:26:56,175 --> 00:26:56,575
Here.

481
00:26:56,656 --> 00:26:57,656
Take two eggs.

482
00:26:57,695 --> 00:26:59,016
- One is enough.
- Not at all.

483
00:27:00,455 --> 00:27:02,496
Now, you're working at Beiya.

484
00:27:02,496 --> 00:27:03,136
Does it mean

485
00:27:03,616 --> 00:27:05,776
you will see Zhiqian every day?

486
00:27:08,095 --> 00:27:09,815
Look at her. What's the hurry?

487
00:27:09,896 --> 00:27:12,055
This world is small, isn't it?

488
00:27:12,256 --> 00:27:15,016
She has been avoiding Zhiqian
for six years.

489
00:27:15,016 --> 00:27:17,295
Yet now they meet again.

490
00:27:17,376 --> 00:27:18,136
I wonder what Liuzheng

491
00:27:18,175 --> 00:27:19,695
thinks about Zhiqian.

492
00:27:19,736 --> 00:27:20,776
Do you know anything?

493
00:27:21,376 --> 00:27:24,095
She always deflects the topic
whenever I mention Zhiqian.

494
00:27:25,175 --> 00:27:26,575
Despite this, I think

495
00:27:26,776 --> 00:27:29,335
both of them are shoved together

496
00:27:29,335 --> 00:27:30,536
by heaven's will.

497
00:27:30,856 --> 00:27:32,695
She can't go against heaven,
can she?

498
00:27:32,856 --> 00:27:34,055
No.

499
00:27:34,175 --> 00:27:35,935
Speaking of which, Zhiqian

500
00:27:35,976 --> 00:27:37,415
is a nice man.

501
00:27:37,415 --> 00:27:38,335
- Am I right?
- Rightfully so.

502
00:27:41,776 --> 00:27:43,455
We must be on the same page this time.

503
00:27:44,215 --> 00:27:45,695
Yes if it's about our consensus,

504
00:27:45,695 --> 00:27:47,575
but not about the food.

505
00:27:47,575 --> 00:27:48,695
I prefer buns.

506
00:27:48,776 --> 00:27:49,376
What an old hat.

507
00:27:57,780 --> 00:28:01,940
(Beiya Hospital)

508
00:28:13,856 --> 00:28:15,175
(The patient on bed twelve
is off an operating table.)

509
00:28:15,215 --> 00:28:17,295
(Do keep a close watch
on the patient's situation.)

510
00:28:17,415 --> 00:28:18,136
Tan Ya.

511
00:28:18,536 --> 00:28:19,215
You're here.

512
00:28:20,896 --> 00:28:21,736
Come with me.

513
00:28:21,736 --> 00:28:22,896
Today is your first day here.

514
00:28:22,896 --> 00:28:24,656
I will show you around.

515
00:28:25,095 --> 00:28:27,055
In Beiya's Neurosurgery Department,
there are four inpatient wards.

516
00:28:27,055 --> 00:28:28,335
Over there, it is Ward 1 and 2.

517
00:28:28,335 --> 00:28:29,815
This site is Ward 3 and 4.

518
00:28:30,136 --> 00:28:32,656
Every ward has its own head.

519
00:28:32,656 --> 00:28:34,656
Currently, the head of Ward 3

520
00:28:34,656 --> 00:28:35,575
remains vacant.

521
00:28:35,616 --> 00:28:37,055
Ning Zhiqian is one of the candidates.

522
00:28:37,856 --> 00:28:39,656
He's not even 35 years old.

523
00:28:39,736 --> 00:28:41,256
How come the hospital
regards him so highly?

524
00:28:41,976 --> 00:28:43,415
Because he is courageous and wise.

525
00:28:43,415 --> 00:28:44,415
He's a skilled neurosurgeon

526
00:28:44,455 --> 00:28:45,376
who stands out

527
00:28:45,376 --> 00:28:46,935
amongst the young doctors.

528
00:28:47,175 --> 00:28:49,136
Besides, he has a great teacher.

529
00:28:49,295 --> 00:28:51,496
That's Liu Chenxi, a legendary character

530
00:28:51,496 --> 00:28:52,815
in the history of Beiya.

531
00:28:55,736 --> 00:29:00,016
Speaking of which,
both of you are quite fated.

532
00:29:00,656 --> 00:29:02,656
No, we have a deeper fate.

533
00:29:03,695 --> 00:29:04,415
Hey.

534
00:29:04,455 --> 00:29:06,695
Don't tell others about our past.

535
00:29:06,896 --> 00:29:08,055
I'm not a gossip.

536
00:29:08,055 --> 00:29:09,055
No, you're.

537
00:29:10,496 --> 00:29:11,896
You know me well though.

538
00:29:11,935 --> 00:29:13,095
Buy me a meal.

539
00:29:13,896 --> 00:29:15,695
You better tell me what you want to eat

540
00:29:15,736 --> 00:29:17,215
so that I can buy your silence.

541
00:29:17,536 --> 00:29:18,776
Watch your purse well.

542
00:29:26,940 --> 00:29:27,900
(Expert Team of Neurosurgery)

543
00:29:32,260 --> 00:29:39,540
(Ning Zhiqian)

544
00:29:45,415 --> 00:29:47,016
Come on,
I'll show you the changing room.

545
00:29:58,415 --> 00:30:00,016
I will introduce
your new colleagues to you.

546
00:30:00,935 --> 00:30:02,415
Guys, over here.

547
00:30:02,496 --> 00:30:03,896
Let me introduce her to you.

548
00:30:03,896 --> 00:30:05,736
She's seconded to work here

549
00:30:05,736 --> 00:30:07,055
from West District Hospital.

550
00:30:07,055 --> 00:30:08,496
Her name is Ruan Liuzheng.

551
00:30:08,496 --> 00:30:09,736
Let's welcome her.

552
00:30:10,815 --> 00:30:12,496
Hello, I'm Ruan Liuzheng.

553
00:30:12,496 --> 00:30:13,935
Please look out for me.

554
00:30:13,976 --> 00:30:15,415
It's been a while, Dr. Ruan.

555
00:30:15,415 --> 00:30:16,935
Do you still remember me?
I'm Wu Xiaofan.

556
00:30:17,016 --> 00:30:17,976
Dr. Wu.

557
00:30:19,656 --> 00:30:21,896
Finally, a female doctor comes.

558
00:30:21,896 --> 00:30:22,856
Let me introduce myself.

559
00:30:22,856 --> 00:30:23,575
I'm Bai Jun,

560
00:30:23,616 --> 00:30:25,575
the chief resident.

561
00:30:25,695 --> 00:30:26,736
The unattached bachelor.

562
00:30:26,776 --> 00:30:27,376
